<help general wear>

Attempt to utilize a piece of your inventory.  You gain the
benefits and or penalties of the piece of equipment. 

Syntax:  wear <<i_th> [item] [position]

Example:  wear gloves
	  wear gloves hands
	  wear 2.ring finger
	  wear all
<color = red>
See Also:  remove, wield, hold
</color></help>
